changelog.version: Hanako has joined the game! Cammy has been reworked!
Miko, Ini, Coco, Rarity, Franziska, and Sayaka have joined the game! Sheena has been reworked! Added support for characters using the Pose Engine.
Lotte, Kizuna AI, Haru, Jotaro, Cammy, Sayori, Pinkie Pie and Kamina have joined the game! Also re-sorted the character roster.
Natsuki, Catria, Mulan, Remilia and Navi have joined the game! Also adds the alternate costume selector to the offline version of the game.
Beatrix, Juri, Jolyne, Shimakaze, Ryuji, and Nayru have joined the game!
Black Canary has joined the game!
Launch, Kira, and Monika have joined the game!
Velma and Amalia have returned to the game!
